('ai-analyzer',      'overview', 'description', 'Product Description', 'Awalife AI Series Morphology Analyzer is an AI-powered veterinary platform for four sample types: blood, urine, feces, and body fluids. It combines multi-focus imaging, rapid liquid-based staining, AI-assisted morphology recognition and counting, and report generation with review-ready images and quantitative results. The system also supports an expandable parameter set for deeper clinical insight.', 'text'),

